Aimee Brooks https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Aimee_Brooks 0 Aimee Brooks (born November 19, 1974) is an American actress. She is mostly known for her roles in horror movies, including the lead protagonist in Critters 3. Her most recent film is Closed for the Season in 2010. Aimee Brooks also appeared in the television series Valerie, Blossom, Eerie, Indiana, Brooklyn Bridge, Criminal Minds, Shark and was a series regular in the sitcom Muddling Through.
